luogo="Parigi"#see basic program - 1 to understand how its working
eta="34"#see basic program - 1 to understand how its working
#we can also write eta=34, because 34 has a numerical value
frase="ciao, abito a {} e ho {} anni".format(luogo,eta)
#using the format, we can give the first content to the first {}, the second content to the second {} ...
#so in the first {} (... abito a {} e ...) we give the content that is in luogo and becomes (... abito a Parigi e ...)
print (frase)#see basic program - 1 to understand how its working
